<p>Two fragments from the top of a<rs type="material"> white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> with damaged moulding. a: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.22</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.19</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.10</measure>. b: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.18</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.15</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.09</measure>.</p>
</div>
